Use the standard library
This is how to words_string of s:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that current is ""
   Remember that i is 0

   Do this s's length times:
      Remember that ch is item i in s
      When ch is item 0 in " ", then:
         When current's length is more than 0, then:
            Add result to current
            Remember that current is ""
         End when
      But, if not:
         When ch is item 0 in ",", then:
            When current's length is more than 0, then:
               Add result to current
               Remember that current is ""
            End when
         But, if not:
            Add current to ch
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   When current's length is more than 0, then:
      Add result to current
   End when

   The answer is result
